          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-mark-todd" title="Mr Mark Todd">Mr. Todd</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            My hon. Friend has spoken to me.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0387P1_20020618_WH_73'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-chidgey' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0387P1_20020618_WH_73' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Chidgey' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
